title: UIExtension错误码
summary: ArkUI ArkUI 模块的 UIExtension错误码，提供相关接口和功能说明。

sections.title: 1011 Ability启动失败
sections.summary:
**错误信息**

Failed to start the UIExtension ability.

**错误描述**

扩展Ability拉起失败，请检查扩展Ability的Want参数。

*

sections.title: 1012 Ability切后台失败
sections.summary:
**错误信息**

Failed to switch the UIExtension ability to the background.

**错误描述**

扩展Ability切后台失败。

*

sections.title: 1013 Ability终止失败
sections.summary:
**错误信息**

Failed to destroy the UIExtension ability.

**错误描述**

扩展Ability终止失败。

**可能原因**

扩展Ability

sections.title: 100011 未注册同步回调
sections.summary:
**错误信息**

No callback has been registered to respond to this request.

**错误描述**

扩展Ability未注册同步回调。

sections.title: 100012 数据发送失败
sections.summary:
**错误信息**

Transferring data failed.

**错误描述**

数据发送失败。

**可能原因**

数据发送失败，需根据AMS日志具体分析。

**处理步骤**

根

sections.summary:

**错误描述**

拉取另一个嵌入式组件失败，UIExtension存在特殊场
